Uber
Title : Userâ€™s Third Transaction

Task : Write a query to obtain the third transaction of every user. Output the user id, spend and transaction date.
transactions Table:

Column Name	      | Type
user_id	          | integer
spend	            | decimal
transaction_date	| timestamp

Example Output:

user_id	    | spend	   |transaction_date
111	        | 89.60	   | 02/05/2022 12:00:00

Solution

WITH trans_num AS (
  SELECT 
    user_id, 
    spend, 
    transaction_date, 
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
      PARTITION BY user_id ORDER BY transaction_date) AS row_num 
  FROM transactions)
 
SELECT 
  user_id, 
  spend, 
  transaction_date 
FROM trans_num 
WHERE row_num = 3;
